      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.themes.Item.xDbfdvvSm1Yw5JUg]{Battle Medic}</p>\n<p>You are known for the quality of healing that you can provide to a patient even under imperfect circumstances. When you successfully ensure a creatureâ€™s long-term stability with the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.d4fcGwOcrsuYrwGH]{Medicine} skill, you grant the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.lf8pbezocjYIvR9y]{Unconscious} creature a +4 bonus to their Constitution check (instead of +2). In addition, when you successfully provide @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.d4fcGwOcrsuYrwGH#long-term-care]{long-term} care with the Medicine skill, you need to exceed the DC by only 5 to have the patient recover Hit Points and ability score damage (as well as recovering from poison states) at three times the normal rate.</p>"
